products.name: -- About App --
products.description:
Hope you enjoyed ANZ product details on your wrist (fitbit) !

`My Bank -AU-9` app displays products offered by ANZ Bank (Australia).

Data is provided available as per Consumer Data Right (ACCC), Australia (alos known as Open Banking).

List of products displayed may not contain all the products currently offered by the bank.
Hence, for making any financial decision always go to : https://www.ANZ.com.au/
